# I can prepare to be baptized

<center>
<img src="baptism.jpg" width="600"/>
</center>

* What do we have to do to be baptized?

## Moroni 6:2

> Neither did they receive any unto baptism save they came forth with a broken
> heart and a contrite spirit, and witnessed unto the church that they truly
> repented of all their sins.

# I am blessed when I go to church

<center>
<img src="church.png" width="600"/>
</center>


## Moroni 6:5

> And the church did meet together oft, to fast and to pray, and to speak one
> with another concerning the welfare of their souls.

